Key Match Events: Trae Young drained a game-winning half-court shot
Miscellaneous Highlights: This look at Jazz fans going from elation to shock within a matter of seconds is priceless.
Others: Trae Young finished with 24 points, 20 assists, and 3-of-10 3-pointers. Clint Capela scored 18 points on 9-for-11 shooting. De'Andre Hunter scored 17 points off the bench and Dyson Daniels added 16. Lauri Markkanen scored 35 points on 11-for-21 shooting while drilling eight 3-pointers. Collin Sexton added 24 for the Jazz, including the game-tying bucket, and Walker Kessler scored 21.
